    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an immaculate 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2), a true driver\u2019s specification featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six engine. This unit has been fastidiously maintained, with a documented LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and recent bore-scope verification ensuring mechanical integrity. The G96/01 six-speed manual transmission provides tactile, precise shifts, while the factory-spec suspension maintains its original geometry for exceptional lateral grip and turn-in response. The exterior retains its factory luster with zero swirls or imperfections, and the interior exhibits no bolster wear or soft-touch plastic degradation. This example delivers a linear power band and a mechanical purity that modern electronic systems cannot replicate.",
      "price": 48500.0,
